OL,5, A woman who was sexually harassed by   
OL,6, her boss as a teen has urged other     
OL,7, girls not to put up with such          
OL,8, behaviour.                             
OL,10,FAlona Forose was 15 in 2017 when she   
OL,11,Fworked part-time in Scoopy Sweets and  
OL,12,FIce-cream shop in Armagh.              
OL,14,FShe has been awarded more than #54,000 
OL,15,Fafter the Court of Appeal upheld an    
OL,16,Fearlier industrial tribunal's judgment.
OL,18,FMs Forose said Eugene Geraghty, who was
OL,19,Fthen in his late 50s, inappropriately  
OL,20,Ftouched and smacked her.               
